Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全球排名第一的TAKANO_EYE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱理？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  八汐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是GEZI姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在观测实验的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  日本标准时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公元2019年8月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验编号为2946
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是使用EGI系统进行的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  向着天空发射那段噪音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  实验的结果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  马上就要得出结果了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是磁单极子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…原来是磁单极子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西
